  "title": "Facilities & Admin Coordinator | 5 days - AMK [0580]",
  "description": "<ul><li>Working days: Monday - Friday 830am to 530pm</li><li>Working Location : Ang Mo Kio</li><li>Salary: $2,800 - $3200</li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in office facilities and maintenance requirements by scheduling, assigning and follow up with vendor/contactors on work progress</li><li>Undertake and oversee office renovation projects and work with various vendors/ contractors to ensure completion</li><li>Assist in enhancing office efficiency by planning and implementing office systems, layouts, and safety equipment’s procurement</li><li>Recommend any improvements to reduce cost or increase efficiency of the facilities services</li><li>Responsible in the general office management like yearly carpet and office cleaning service</li><li>Assist with Building Management FSM to conduct and coordinate fire drill - CERT exercise</li><li>Support Production and Engineering departments on facilities maintenance, not limited to yearly disposal of expired chemical and damaged equipment under the compliance procedure</li><li>Track and update planned preventive maintenance schedule. Manage quarterly/ yearly renewal and compliance of necessary building and facilities permits and inspections</li><li>Organize and maintain proper facilities management documentation and records</li><li>Provide Office Admin support</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>At least 2 years of relevant working experience</li><li>Proficient in MS Office software</li><li>Willing to do hands-on work such as packing, checking and organizing stock items</li></ul><p><br />The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd || 14C7279</p><p>Chua Jie Ying (Cai Jie Ying), Evelynn || EA Personnel License R24120580</p>",
